{"id":"a246101c-997d-4f11-b299-6c4394fd535e","name":"Best Friends/Rivals: Raine Clearsky and Cyra Daylight","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(42, 90, 255)\"><strong><em>\"Cyra, thanks for coming to help.\"</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 42, 42)\"><strong><em>\"Don’t mention it, Raine.\"</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>Aetherspark College: a prestigious institution dedicated to unlocking the potential of its students.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>Its renown stems from the countless brilliant minds it has cultivated—and continues to inspire.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>These bright sparks hail from all walks of life, perfectly embodied by two extraordinary students: Raine Clearsky and Cyra Daylight.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>Raine, a talented mage, was born to a humble commoner family.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>Cyra, by contrast, is a prodigy from the esteemed and powerful Daylight Order.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>What unites them is the remarkable skill and determination that earned their place at Aetherspark.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>Few realize, however, that these two are more than rivals—they’re also inseparable best friends.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(42, 90, 255)\"><strong><em>Friends</em></strong></span><strong><em>/</em></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 42, 42)\"><strong><em>Dumbasses</em></strong></span><strong><em>:</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/8f332e6f-b405-4925-b91e-d80b617b9b6a_b0a06b41-370b-4b69-a750-636aac825ce5.webp?width=1000\"><span style=\"color: rgb(42, 90, 255)\"><strong>